text: Joseph Henry (1797–1878) was an American scientist. Joseph Henry may also refer to: *Joseph Henry (politician) (1853–1894), New Zealand Member of Parliament *Joseph Henry (bow maker) (1823–1870), French bow maker *Joe Henry (born 1960), Grammy-award-winning American musician *Joe Henry (baseball) (1930–2009), American baseball player *The Joseph Henry, a mine-planting ship of the U.S. Army *Joseph Henry Press, an American publisher named after the scientist
title: Joseph Henry (disambiguation)
